From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix AutoMapper 12.x/13.x version conflict in DT.Api

The DT.Api project referenced AutoMapper.Extensions.Microsoft.DependencyInjection
12.0.1, which pins AutoMapper to exactly 12.0.1. DT.Application requires
AutoMapper >= 13.0.1, causing a restore conflict.

Resolution:
- Add a direct reference to AutoMapper 13.0.1 in DT.Api.
- Upgrade AutoMapper.Extensions.Microsoft.DependencyInjection to 13.0.1,
  which is compatible with AutoMapper 13.0.1.

---
 src/DT.Api/DT.Api.csproj | 3 ++-
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/src/DT.Api/DT.Api.csproj b/src/DT.Api/DT.Api.csproj
--- a/src/DT.Api/DT.Api.csproj
+++ b/src/DT.Api/DT.Api.csproj
@@
   <ItemGroup>
-    <PackageReference Include="AutoMapper.Extensions.Microsoft.DependencyInjection" Version="12.0.1" />
+    <PackageReference Include="AutoMapper" Version="13.0.1" />
+    <PackageReference Include="AutoMapper.Extensions.Microsoft.DependencyInjection" Version="13.0.1" />
     <PackageReference Include="Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authentication.JwtBearer" Version="8.0.0" />
     <PackageReference Include="Microsoft.AspNetCore.OpenApi" Version="8.0.0" />
     <PackageReference Include="Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Design" Version="8.0.0">
